<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1- tsbyḥ llrb yʿly̱ .. wtʿly̱ mʿạh ạlfrḥẗ
 qlby hygẖny llqdyr
 bạ̹ymạny hạsẖwf ạlkẖyr .. fy ẓrwfy ḥty̱ ạlṣʿbẗ
 gẖny yạ nfsy llqdyr
 bạʿln ạ̹ymạny sẖạyf ạ̹lhy .. (lyh ạlslṭạn)2
 wmn ạ̉mạmy ynql jbạly .. (bạlạ̹ymạn)2
 (ạ̉nạ hạfrḥ wạhtf mjdaⁿạ lyk mjdaⁿạ lyk mjdaⁿạ lyk)2
 hllwyạ .. hllwyạ .. hllwyạ .. hllwyạ
 2- bạʿln yswʿ mlk wḥyd .. ʿly̱ kl ḥyạty
 qlby hygẖny llmsyḥ
 wbṣwt ạlḥmd rạḥ ạsẖhd lh .. ttẖbt ṣlạty
 gẖny yạ nfsy llmsyḥ
 ʿmry wḥyạty kl ạ̉hdạfy .. (llmsyḥ)2
 wlywm mjyỷh hạstny̱ ạ̉sẖwfh .. (fy ạlạ̉mjạd)2
 (ạ̉nạ frḥạn bạhtf mjdaⁿạ lyk mjdaⁿạ lyk mjdaⁿạ lyk)2
 hllwyạ .. hllwyạ .. hllwyạ .. hllwyạ</lyrics>
